    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have to see this absolute dream of a car. It\u2019s in truly pristine condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this beauty from day one, and it really shows in every single detail. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s practically perfect and ready for the road, this is definitely the one for you. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel!",
