      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that defies its age. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, retaining its deep, mirror-like factory finish thanks to a professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the premium leather seats show zero bolster wear, and every switchgear operates with a satisfying, factory-new tactile feel. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, boasting a complete, documented service history from day one. It drives exactly as it did when it first rolled off the lot\u2014tight, responsive, and whisper-quiet. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or enthusiast to own a vehicle that has been loved rather than just driven. Non-smoker, no pets, and always hand-washed with the finest products.",
