      "description": "Hey there! You have got to see this absolute beauty. I\u2019ve taken incredible care of it, and honestly, it\u2019s in such pristine, showroom-level condition that it feels just like driving it off the lot for the first time! It\u2019s been garage-kept, spotless inside and out, and drives like an absolute dream. I'm looking for a great new home for it\u2014if you want a ride that\u2019s basically brand new, this is the one for you. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
